      "review_summary": "The PR adds a typed pre-prompt context-budget snapshot to embedded-agent metadata, persists it on session entries, exposes it on gateway session rows, and renders it as a `/status` fallback when fresh usage is absent.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review finding: source inspection shows reset helpers retain the new field while clearing token usage, and `/status` uses that field when totals are missing or zero. I did not run tests because this was a read-only review.",
